VPN - Virtual Private Network.
Purpose -> safe delivary of data across public network
Working -> VPN  Client installed in the System establishes a VPN Tunnel within the public network which then connects to VPN Server & from there it connects to Company Server.
Benifits -> Anonymity ( hiding my identity -location, IP etc )
            Privacy ( hiding the activity - which websites are visited , what work was done ) 
-: no log policy VPN is more safe

